{"tid":2004132,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"翻牆你們自己玩！《決勝時刻》VPN的全當外掛　對岸玩家哭：我們權益在哪","createTime":"2020-05-06T08:52:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-06T14:49:45.000Z","uid":282053,"like":33,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"69506d2828dc1d3d4fdef8556c237fe2c2e88995","tid":2004132,"uid":282053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T08:52:44.000Z","msg":"射擊遊戲《決勝時刻：現代戰爭》近期推出大型競技場《決勝時刻：現代戰域》，因為外掛的氾濫嚴重影響玩家體驗，因此開發商Infinity Ward就在近日公布了全新的外掛打擊措施，將引進最先進的連線偵測系統，若發現玩家疑似作弊，就會把他們排到同一場遊戲對戰中。<br />\n<br />\n也許是發現大多數作弊都是使用VPN伺服器的亞太玩家，因此只要系統偵測到有使用VPN連線，系統就會有很高機率將玩家排到「作弊房」一起玩。<br />\n<br />\n「這種作弊行為是絕對不允許的，維持遊戲環境與公平性是我們最重視的事情之一。」Infinity Ward如此說著。<br />\n<br />\n而這個鐵腕政策一祭出之後，大批的對岸玩家卻紛紛哀號大叫「根本不能玩了」，一名來自對岸的Youtuber就發了影片官方的做法不恰當「動視就是蠢驢，每個國家都有作弊的人，把我們這些乖乖玩的玩家通通跟作弊者放一起，這是恰當的事情嗎？為什麼不學學CSGO．．．或者其他的遊戲？」一名對岸玩家在影片中激動的說著。<br />\n<br />\n看到遊戲影片後，許多PTT的鄉民紛紛表示：<br />\n<br />\n「笑死，只能打外掛。」<br />\n<br />\n「沒開掛的會很生氣正常拉。」<br />\n<br />\n「動森就說了不讓你們亂跑出來玩齁」<br />\n<br />\n事實上《決勝時刻：現代戰域》並沒有在中國大陸地區上市，也就是說對岸玩家如果想要玩遊戲，用VPN、加速器翻牆出來玩是唯一途徑，但動視的做法無疑是把所有對岸玩家通通當作「外掛」來處理，這也使大批中國玩家紛紛不滿。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8f6a4e37e5e99ae4ec389ac475facbd59d70c9a","tid":2004132,"uid":209248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T08:54:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d22249cb72b8946b632feb51e45b5b586c9a99e","tid":2004132,"uid":282053,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T08:54:08.000Z","msg":"共雪都出招<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6df9aef5f7b178946ec424a7007132bf5cad4a32","tid":2004132,"uid":998,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T08:54:41.000Z","msg":"Blizzard activision 奶共之後蝕左幾錢？"},{"pid":"aecdeae872b872c29fdca39919cb6c3c01621fc5","tid":2004132,"uid":48357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T08:56:13.000Z","msg":"支那豚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f797ddb753bc2d67a5ec0b8d8aefbe6f44be5e5f","tid":2004132,"uid":11962,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T08:56:59.000Z","msg":"可以玩了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29aba58fb0aed33a318b279aca947f696c2e5ad2","tid":2004132,"uid":185872,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T08:59:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7fd80f85c303b289f05929fd3d5fc1a1c61c97b","tid":2004132,"uid":130197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T09:00:07.000Z","msg":"等睇神仙打架 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"907a3faae77a841ae3b849138467f71daa55e355","tid":2004132,"uid":263534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T09:03:05.000Z","msg":"支那豬學人講權益<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df7dafc762881f67e7e17f3db39dd911b0f94b76","tid":2004132,"uid":109557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T09:26:42.000Z","msg":"解決方法好易啫   自己都down返個外掛玩"},{"pid":"6da3a6eac7d4452b24f31cc8ea2c81dc7de14343","tid":2004132,"uid":60655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T09:49:24.000Z","msg":"除左中國人，邊個打cod會用vpn"},{"pid":"19445bbf835489b13ae02b15f7a7846adba70785","tid":2004132,"uid":